14	- `.stitch/system/META.md` — Reference examples metadata
15	
16	## Steps
17	
18	1. **Read spec** — Load `.stitch/designs/library/SPEC.md` to understand layout, sections, data
19	2. **Read glossary** — Load `stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md` to understand the constrained vocabulary
